Ocster Backup is a great and easy to use application to backup your files. The main focus developers made to fully automate the process. You simply specify who you want zabekapit and at what time, and the program will do everything Ocster Backup itself.

Create backups of your documents and files (stored on your computer or on the network). You can use special network service, Ocster Secure Storage, which can store large amount of data encrypted on the latest technologies. Thus you protect documents from loss (eg, in the case of system failure, etc.).

Program features:
Fully automatic operation
Easy to use
Pause and start again: backup, you can pause at any time and start from the same point, even after reboot
Reports backup: reports can be created each time you create a backup copy of the data. Reports can also be automatically sent by email
Network Support: backups on network drives
Encryption and the ability to compress data
Incremental backups
Open File Support
Support hard and symbolic links.
